creator: Developer@Seeley
descriptionHtml:
Control your MagIQtouch heating and cooling needs directly from your pocket, wherever you are. Using your MagIQtouch Wi-Fi smart app, you can monitor and modify your settings instantly.

Syncing with the innovative MagIQtouch wall controller, you can:
- view the live status of your unit
- turn the system on/off
- adjust temperatures
- adjust fan speeds
- override Program Modes
- fully control room zoning

An installed MagIQtouch wall controller & Wi-Fi module will be compatible with the below appliances:
- Breezair, Braemar and Coolair Evaporative Coolers
- Braemar Ducted Gas Heaters
descriptionShort: Requires an additional Wi-Fi module & compatible MagIQtouch wall controller
